be careful with this cause I download it, it was safe, I didn't crack it, but I did have some serial numbers that worked but Adobe contacted me and said that the serial number was no longer available to use to eater put in a new number or buy the license or use the 30 day trial. So Im not sure what happens if you crack it, but I do know what happens when you put in a fake keygen code, I tried it with 2 numbers and they caught me both times.
